# SendSprint Plugin

When the user asks to run SendSprint, deliver a sprint, process Jira/Azure DevOps work, or open the local SendSprint dashboard, use the Python CLI.

## Commands

```bash
sendsprint doctor
sendsprint web
sendsprint sprint
sendsprint full --workspace workspace.yaml
sendsprint run jira 42 --workspace workspace.yaml --scope mine
sendsprint run azuredevops "Project\\Team\\Sprint 12" --workspace workspace.yaml
```

## Rules

- Do not reimplement the SendSprint 10-step flow inside Cursor.
- Use `sendsprint web` for localhost monitoring.
- Use `sendsprint full --workspace workspace.yaml` for continuous mode.
- Keep credentials in the OS keyring through SendSprint login/auth flows.
- Report PR URL, run report, evidence, blockers, and next actions.

